:<font size="15">סדם</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
סדם / sedôm / sed-ome'

===Etymology===
From an unused root meaning to scorch; 

===Proper noun===
'''סדם'''

# [[burnt]] (that is, volcanic or bituminous) district; Sedom, a place near the Dead Sea: - [[Sodom]].

